a “Exam Countdown” note taped to the side,  
and a small motivational line: “One small step a day!”
===
title: GirlsDesk
---
(A lively, talkative girl’s desk.)
Covered in cute stickers and a lip balm.  
Hina:They talked about idols every break.  
Mio joined sometimes…  
But she always held back a little.
Hina:Everyone has their own worries.  
But Mio never talked about hers.
===
