title: WindowView
---
(Outside the window: the field after PE class.  
Chalk dust still floats in the air.)
A few pigeons wander across the track.
Hina:Mio said she liked how pigeons walk.
(A faint jingle echoes from somewhere far away—barely audible.)
Hina:…That sound again.
